
    <main class="container py-4">
<div class="row g-3">
  <div class="col-lg-7">
    <div class="card shadow-sm h-100">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="h5 mb-3">收件資料</h2>
        <form id="checkout-form">
          <div class="row g-3">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <label class="form-label">姓名</label>
              <input class="form-control" name="FullName" required>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <label class="form-label">Email</label>
              <input type="email" class="form-control" name="Email" required>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <label class="form-label">電話</label>
              <input class="form-control" name="Phone" required>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12">
              <label class="form-label">收件地址</label>
              <input class="form-control" name="Address" required>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-end mt-3">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">送出訂單</button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-lg-5">
    <div class="card shadow-sm h-100">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="h5 mb-3">訂單摘要</h2>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
          <div>小計</div>
          <div class="fw-semibold">$<span id="checkout-total">0</span></div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <p class="text-secondary small mb-0">此為示範頁面。實務上按下「送出訂單」後，會呼叫後端API建立訂單、扣庫存、並導向成功頁。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
    </main>